---
title: Smart Eggy BLT and Chicken Breasts Salad with DIY Caesar-ish Dressing and Garlic Croutons
description: Everyone's favourite salad, but with a spicy twist! Crispy bacon, marinated tomatoes and rustic croutons are the stars of this speedy dinner. Our creamy DIY garlic-parmesan dressing will have your tastebuds on their toes.
